20946005@unknown@formal@none@1@S@The result was a world-famous trial exposing profound cultural conflicts in American life between the "smart set," whose spokesman was H.L. Mencken, and the religious fundamentalists, whom Mencken derided as benighted primitives.@@@@1@32@@oe@2-2-2013
